'''Dynjandi''' (also known as Fjallfoss) is a series of [[waterfall]]s located in the [[Westfjords]] (Vestfirðir), [[Iceland]]. The waterfalls have a total height of {{convert|100|m|ft}}.<ref>[http://www.world-of-waterfalls.com/iceland-dynjandi.html World of Waterfalls - Dynjandi]</ref>

